<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="cs">
<head>
    <title>
        {ifset title}{include title} | {/ifset} Výfuk
    </title>
    <meta charset="utf-8"/>
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/>
    <meta name="description" content=""/>
    <meta name="author" content=""/>
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#FF7200">

    <meta property="og:type" content="website"/>
    <meta property="og:title" content="Výpočty fyzikálních úkolů"/>
    <meta property="og:image:type" content="image/png"/>
    <meta property="og:locale" content="cs"/>
    <meta property="og:url" content="{plink //this}"/>
    <link href="{$basePath}/images/icon.png" rel="icon" type="image/png"/>
    <link href="{asset 'assets/main.css'}" rel="stylesheet"/>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:ital,wght@0,100;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,700;0,900;1,100;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,700;1,900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"> 
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/f424cd1bbe.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    {block head}{/block}
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.9.3/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-eMNCOe7tC1doHpGoWe/6oMVemdAVTMs2xqW4mwXrXsW0L84Iytr2wi5v2QjrP/xp" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="{asset 'assets/main.js'}"></script>
    {block scripts}{/block}
</head>

<body>

{block body}
    {control navigation "/images/logo.svg", "Vyfuk.org", false}
    <main>
        {block main}
            <div class="panel color-light">
                <section class="inner-container">
                    {ifset subtitle}<div class="subheader">{include subtitle}</div>{/ifset}
                    {ifset title}<h1>{include title}</h1>{/ifset}
                    {include content}
                </section>
            </div>
        {/block}
    </main>
    {*TODO vizuální oddělení main a footer*}
    <hr style="height: 20px; margin: 0px; color: #ff4800; background-color: #ff4800; opacity: 100%">
    <footer>
        <div class="panel sponsors">
            <div class="inner-container">
                <div class="category">
                    <div class="category-title">Pořadatelé</div>
                    <div class="category-sponsors">
                        <a href="https://www.mff.cuni.cz/" style="text-align: center">
                            <img src="{$basePath}/images/logos/mff.png" class="sponsor-logo" alt="MFF logo"
                                style="max-width: 8rem">
                        </a>
                        <a href="https://www.msmt.cz/" style="text-align: center">
                            <img src="{$basePath}/images/logos/msmt_cs.jpg" alt="MŠMT logo" style="max-width: 9rem">
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="category">
                    <div class="category-title">Sponzoři</div>
                    <div class="category-sponsors">
                        <a href="https://www.prusa3d.com/cs" style="text-align: center">
                            <img src="{$basePath}/images/logos/prusa_logo.png" alt="Prusa logo" style="max-height: 5rem; max-width: 12rem">
                        </a>
                        <a href="https://prometheus-nakl.cz/" style="text-align: center">
                            <img src="{$basePath}/images/logos/prometheus_logo.png" alt="Prometheus logo" style="max-height: 5rem; max-width: 12rem">
                        </a>
                        <a href="https://mindok.cz/" style="text-align: center">
                            <img src="{$basePath}/images/logos/mindok_logo.gif" alt="Mindok logo" style="max-height: 5rem; max-width: 12rem">
                        </a>
                        <a href="https://vesmir.cz/cz/" style="text-align: center">
                            <img src="{$basePath}/images/logos/vesmir_logo.png" alt="Vesmír logo" style="max-height: 5rem; max-width: 12rem">
                        </a>
                        <a href="https://cez.cz" style="text-align: center">
                            <img src="{$basePath}/images/logos/cez_logo.png" alt="Čez logo" style="max-height: 5rem; max-width: 12rem">
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel footer">
            <div class="inner-container row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="logo" style="font-size: 1cm; font-weight: bold"><img class="logo" style="margin-right: 1rem; margin-bottom: 0rem" src="{$basePath}/images/logo.svg" alt="Výfuk" />vyfuk<small>.org</small></div>
                    <p>
                        Korespondenční seminář Výfuk je organizován studenty a přáteli <a href="https://www.mff.cuni.cz/">Matematicko-fyzikální fakulty Univerzity Karlovy</a>.
                        Je zastřešen Oddělením propagace a mediální komunikace MFF UK a podporován Katedrou didaktiky
                        fyziky MFF UK, jejími zaměstnanci a Jednotou českých matematiků a fyziků.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Realizace projektu byla podpořena Ministerstvem školství, mládeže a tělovýchovy.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <strong>#vyfuk</strong> <a href="mailto:vyfuk@vyfuk.org">vyfuk@vyfuk.org</a>
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-3">
                    <nav>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Pro účastníky a učitele
                                <ul>
                                    <li><a n:href=":Default:About:default">O Nás</a></li>
                                    <li><a n:href=":Default:Rules:default">Pravidla</a></li>
                                    <li><a n:href=":default">Jak se zapojit</li>
                                    <li><a n:href=":Default:Teachers:default">Pro učitele</li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </nav>
                    <nav>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Pro sponzory
                                <ul>
                                    <li><a n:href=":Default:Sponsors:default">Podpořte nás</a></li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </nav>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-3" style="position: relative">
                    <nav>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Sledujte nás
                                <ul>
                                    <li>
                                    <a style="margin-right: 1.5rem" href="https://www.instagram.com/ksvyfuk/">
                                            <i class="fab fa-instagram fa-2x"></i>
                                        </a>
                                        <a style="margin-right: 1.5rem" href="https://vyfuk.org/discord">
                                            <i class="fab fa-discord fa-2x"></i>
                                        </a>
                                        <a style="margin-right: 1.5rem;" href="https://facebook.com/ksvyfuk">
                                            <i class="fab fa-facebook-f fa-2x"></i>
                                        </a>
                                        <a style="margin-right: 1.5rem" href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCUBv3Ydd-laLSY5DMimoE7w">
                                            <i class="fab fa-youtube fa-2x"></i>
                                        </a>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </nav>
                    <a href="#top"style="position: absolute; bottom: 0; right: 0;"><i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

{/block}
</body>
</html>
